snippet.title: Trine 5: A Clockwork Conspiracy - Couch Co-Op Trailer | PS5 & PS4 Games
snippet.description:
https://store.playstation.com/en-us/concept/10007533/

Let’s go, guys! Grab your controller and team up with up to three friends, online or offline, and push back the fearsome Clockwork army. 

The upgraded puzzle system keeps things fresh, adapting the challenge to the number of players as you traverse the breathtaking 2.5D landscapes in Trine’s latest chapter.

Trine 5: A Clockwork Conspiracy is coming to PlayStation 5 and PlayStation 4 on August 31. 

#ps5 #ps5games #ps4 #ps4games #trine
